---
title: Chargrilled Cheesy Beef & Bacon Charcoal Burgers with Wedges, Charred Pineapple & Avocado Salad
description: You can never, ever go wrong with bacon in a burger, and this recipe is a case in point. Add smoked Cheddar, a juicy beef patty
and charred pineapple, and you're in for a burger that's up there with the best. The wedges feel a bit fancy, too.
